Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.98,Title,,0,0,0,,We Are Mangaka\N{\c&H3C3DFF&}The Story of Tokiwa-sou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}009, Doraemon, Tensai Bakabon, and so on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The authors of these manga, now so familiar\Nto you, spent their youths honing their craft.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our wonderful animation will\Nshowcase those days, full of tears and laughter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coming up — NISSAY Family Special:{see https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%BA}{\i0}{also see https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%A5%E7%94%9F%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%83%9F%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%83%9A%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A3%E3%83%AB}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"We Are Mangaka—The Story of Tokiwa-sou"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please look forward to it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:40.41,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,950)}We Are Mangaka\N{\c&H3C3DFF&}The Story of Tokiwa-sou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:51.51,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,I bet you remember them, too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:58.87,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,The hallways and rooms of that dormitory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:04.56,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,And the rain puddles you saw from the window
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:11.28,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,Though the rain has already let up,{Even in the town where the rain has stopped,}{I hear 雨も上がった街なのに but can't be 100% sure, Yume had it "Ame mo anata machi nanoni = And while you may be waiting for the rain,"}{Y: I agree, minor rewording}
