Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:31.84,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,That's what our youth was all about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:43.96,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,With a squint, you too could also see it{When you closed one eye, \Nyou could see it too}{I hear katame, not tadame, otherwise "kimi wa tada me wo tsubutte miseta ne = Shutting your eyes is all it takes to see that"}{Y: agree, going for a bit more liberal take}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here's a volume of manga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you imagine the shock this tattered\Nbook had on the young minds of bygone days?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was released on April 1st, 1947.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Written by...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.77,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Written by Osamu Tezuka"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Osamushi Tezuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that read as Jimushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jichuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Written by Harumushi Tezuka, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those comics might as\Nwell have been written by a god.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With their own eyes,\Nthe boys saw cars rushing forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With their own ears,\Nthey heard the roar of the engine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What gave this manga such an exciting effect?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The boys had no idea whatsoever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop drawing cartoons\Nall the time! Focus on your studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That you, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.57,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Manga Shounen"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This came in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! "Manga Shounen"—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure to keep it hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Sho. \NYou've been published again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, you're the only\None to ever congratulate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone will appreciate it now. \NYou're on a publishing streak, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You have what it takes to become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sure like to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll have to move to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed it up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This will do. Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it arrive, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He said so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've waited for long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,C-C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.37,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"To: Hiroshi Fujimoto"\N"From: Osamu Tezuka"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here! At last, it arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it'd arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it really is from Mr. Tezuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you so, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he'd answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks our manga's very fun,\Nand even wants us to come visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Visit him? All the way to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out of the question, Abiko! {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fujiko_Fujio#Fujiko_Fujio_A}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, Fujimoto. The two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...are going to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...in order...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...to draw manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Tokiwa-sou dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.81,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Tokiwa-sou"
