Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you!\N-Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Hachigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for that. \NLeave the formalities at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call me Mr. Tera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I help you with your luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Life's going to be\Nlivelier with you guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tezuka's old room is surely \Ntoo small for the two of you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's way too big for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tezuka's deposit really helped us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, we get to use his old desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us, Fujiko Fujio, \Nget to live here from today on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.57,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Beware of fires"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cooking by yourselves, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any utensils?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no proper pot to steam the rice in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This pot right here is good enough.{"okama" is a small pot for daily cooking, "nabe" is a large pot for hot-pot dishes; wording my way around it}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we put the rice in. What next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know when you don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go ask Mr. Tera again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like bothering\Nhim about every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.25,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Encyclopedia"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An encyclopedia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty pricey for a second-hand book. \NI bet it’s got a section on cooking rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto! What's wrong? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The rice cooked nicely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be the first people to ever\Nuse an encyclopedia as a rice-cooking guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:06.68,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Encyclopedia"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, are you Fujiko Fujio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.20,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Manga Shounen"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rookie of the Year from Manga Shounen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My pen name's Kazetarou.{https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%88%B4%E6%9C%A8%E4%BC%B8%E4%B8%80}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mr. Tera told us about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You live in Tokiwa-sou too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The more, the merrier! Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, which way to Tokiwa-sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiwa-sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you get there! {meaning "follow the shape of the barrel"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,001!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Tokiwa-sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Terada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Onodera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Name's Ishimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{故郷の石森町. Leaving it as is.}Your pen name's\NKuni no Ishimori-Chou, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Fujio Akatsuka. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so you came already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Together with Mr. Akatsuka, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to become\Neven livelier around here.{liberal}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Tezuka used to live in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he leave these marks with his thumbtacks?{画鋲}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to breathe the same air as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!\NDon't waste all the precious air!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See the moldy spot over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the drunken editor used to urinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-He could reach pretty far, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I reach that far...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Anything but that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up with this hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tezuka must've kicked through in his sleep. {not exactly but makes more sense this way}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That was one impressive kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready to celebrate your moving. Come to Mr. Tera's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-About time! \N-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shush. An editor is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What manga would you like me to draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's simple... \NSomething that sells, something popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are popularity and sales all that matters to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thought has never crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A manga should speak to the\Nchildren's hearts, and grasp their imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a proper manga should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You put it like that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A manga which grasps the children's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One that connects with the children's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, did we ever consider any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been drawing what I wanted.\N Nothing else to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come right in, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's draw manga that can\Nkeep the children truly entertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...and fun manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga offers unlimited freedom of expression!{paraphrased}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring manga to a whole new level,\Nwith adventures and experiments!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As for my manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of manga would I like to draw...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{"yaru zo"}We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more of those slackers living up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Keep it down, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A sorry lot of adults obsessed with cartoons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For your information, I'm worried\Nabout the future of Japanese literature!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{likely some Bakabon's catchphrase? Liberal, no idea if there's an official english rendition. "kita naa mou, kita kita hora mou na, bo-boku no kokoro de kiteta naa mou"; I've watched some of it too but that's some truly arcane knowledge right there}I'm feeling it for real!\NRight here in m-muh heart!{Aku- Changed the line slightly, this character's speaking gimmick is hard to translate, but he uses "poku" rather than "boku".}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aku - Catchphrase he often uses, nonsense words for the most part}-Pokkun pokkun!\N-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not too\Nembarrassing as a farewell gift. {餞別}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not!\NYou made it for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the very first\Nperson to praise my manga, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TLC, some catchphrase based on 毛虫?; no idea, seems like more of arcane knowledge; it's https://www.koredeiinoda.net/manga/s_kemunpasu.html btw}Achoo! Kemunpas-choo! Achoo!{Y: Some of these creatures just say their names; the rest is "keshon" as in "hakushon"}{Aku - Not to be excessive in notes, but changed it slightly to mirror the original line.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what are you doing?{"donna shiteru no, nani nani"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...! {"are"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On cold days, stay in your bedroll to keep warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Topsy-turvy!{"denguri"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuu. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, even a single futon can keep you warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're an apprentice to\Nsome wise hermit! So philosophical! {"nanka sennin ga shugyou shiteiru you de, tetsugaku-teki datta"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuu's the real weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's obsessed with animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You know,\Nthe movies with moving drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Making those is a very painstaking job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I'd like to make some, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm nowhere near as good as Fuu is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We poke each other with\Na pen if we doze off, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the promise, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wanna fight?!\N-Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The editor's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need one more day to wrap this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We surrender! {無条件降伏}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our deepest apologies! It isn't ready yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If at all p-possible, please give us one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.95,0:23:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just me, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:03.88,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Bread"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tera!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought snacks.{your rations.} \NStarving won't do your health any good!{Y: rations sounds hella stiff here, softening it up a bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat this with just one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate Mr. Tera's gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But after surviving on nothing but bread\Nfor days, even the sight of it makes me uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:33.70,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Year-End Big Sale"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.50,0:23:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Akatsuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home. I'll be back in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of luggage you've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Souvenirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that. \NWell, have a happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.69,0:24:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going home to do laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can do better!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can win this! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.52,0:24:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.93,0:24:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped five yen down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.09,0:24:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what should I buy with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.12,0:24:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I have to my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.72,0:24:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has to last me for a week, \Nuntil Mr. Ishimori returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.31,0:25:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I buy with 28 yen?\N This calls for careful consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.59,0:25:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.13,0:25:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cook some soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.73,0:25:14.51,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Soy sauce"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.05,0:25:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I slice it super thin, \Nit'll look like there's more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.43,0:25:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a tad too thin?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.88,0:25:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.31,0:25:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stretch this until Mr. Ishimori comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.84,0:25:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.99,0:25:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.22,0:25:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.80,0:25:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out you're the only tenant\N who stayed here for the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.21,0:25:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.13,0:25:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going home too, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.27,0:26:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. My wife and \Nchildren did, but I have unfinished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.54,0:26:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.52,0:26:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Life isn't easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.03,0:26:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I can't even\Nget a break during the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.65,0:26:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.30,0:26:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.82,0:26:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.23,0:26:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, don't concern yourself with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.16,0:26:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that, I wouldn't\Nmind some to warm up my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.61,0:26:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.75,0:26:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel warmer already.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.21,0:26:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the taste isn't half bad either! This soup is something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.92,0:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.43,0:26:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How about another serving?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.61,0:26:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could've guessed\Nyou were this great of a cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.43,0:26:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help myself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.54,0:26:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.69,0:27:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up staying for dinner. \NSorry for imposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.62,0:27:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.35,0:27:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-I look forward to working with you next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.07,0:27:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sure. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.21,0:27:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It could as well have been licked clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.85,0:27:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.02,0:27:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have what it takes to draw a real \Nmasterpiece one day. I can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.67,0:27:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to be working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.12,0:27:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Little World of Don Camillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.69,0:27:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Caine Mutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.58,0:28:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, this will keep the drafts away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.42,0:28:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And done.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.50,0:28:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels no different from a bedroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.15,0:28:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to\Nget by starting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.63,0:28:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I give up on cooking \Nand survive on mochi alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.33,0:28:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stand winters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.09,0:28:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer can't come any sooner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.19,0:28:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer has come! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.91,0:28:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aku - "no ni mo, yama ni mo, hoe hoe to"}Be it plains or mountains,\Nthe summer rolls on through!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.64,0:28:47.64,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Ice"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.36,0:28:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.36,0:29:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.42,0:29:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a desk, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.82,0:29:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I need one, yet I can't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.37,0:29:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.50,0:29:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a sheet of plywood stashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.14,0:29:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.68,0:29:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.93,0:29:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And done!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.96,0:29:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,An Akatsuka-style budget desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.11,0:29:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I just gotta wait for a new client.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.03,0:30:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta hurry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.54,0:30:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You here, Mr. Ishimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.71,0:30:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fujiko, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.47,0:30:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Terada! Mr. Tsuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.86,0:30:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone will do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.84,0:30:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, could you draw a\Npanel for me? This is urgent! {/cut}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.96,0:30:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've been waiting\Nfor it. It'll be done in a jiffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.14,0:30:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go all out. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.43,0:30:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.41,0:30:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At last, my chance has come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.55,0:30:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I manage to capitalize on it,\N I'll be hired as a monthly author!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.09,0:30:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka? What's on your mind,\NMr. Akatsuka? Keep drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.38,0:30:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay. I'll make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.47,0:30:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.22,0:30:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost done. Full steam ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.52,0:31:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.34,0:31:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do. Sorry,\N but I'll have to find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.34,0:31:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.77,0:31:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all! If only I had a proper desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.16,0:31:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.84,0:31:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyarome!{https://www.koredeiinoda.net/manga/s_nyarome.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.73,0:32:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.21,0:32:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.57,0:32:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to cool off, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.32,0:32:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too broke to go to a bathhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.45,0:33:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't replace a real bath, though. {TLC, "furo-dai --chatta mon da kara" as in "I wasted all of my bathing money..." ish?; I have no idea either, could be kechi, then he implies that Ishimori can afford going to the bathhouse, and he can't, but it's still a stretch}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.13,0:33:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it'll do just fine. This is more\Nrelaxing than a trip to a bathhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.08,0:33:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Pure bliss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.12,0:33:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.68,0:33:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.81,0:33:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just catch a\Ncold and leave me hanging!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.58,0:33:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've reserved the pages for your chapter...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.00,0:33:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll have it done in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.51,0:33:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.\NOur dorm is full of people who could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.70,0:33:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold you to your word, Mr. Ishimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.61,0:33:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd better hurry up...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.41,0:33:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My head...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.55,0:34:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Was last night's makeshift bath a bad idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.57,0:34:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.39,0:34:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,SOS!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.20,0:34:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.78,0:34:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...{"de yansu" from "de gozaimasu", liberal}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.54,0:34:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In times of need,\Npersevere and support each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.44,0:34:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, be nice to animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.98,0:34:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nagatani is here! The cavalry has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.33,0:34:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you catch a cold, Mr. Ishimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.21,0:34:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.22,0:34:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.51,0:34:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.57,0:34:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.00,0:34:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka, the outlines are all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.15,0:34:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the finishing touches...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.20,0:35:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.20,0:35:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.21,0:35:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're working so fast, despite the fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.08,0:35:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.38,0:35:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.48,0:35:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if you got sick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.71,0:35:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens,\NI'll simply ask you to lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.71,0:35:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you working\Non these days, Mr. Akatsuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.14,0:35:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.62,0:35:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A volume of a shoujo manga. \NI've managed to land an order at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.61,0:35:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.39,0:35:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Having been bullied by her\Nstepmother, a girl runs away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.82,0:36:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being chased by a gang, enters a\Ncircus troupe, and breaks her legs in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.28,0:36:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.22,0:36:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a stale, cliched story would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.66,0:36:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.91,0:36:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of this is wrong...\NThis isn't the story I want to write.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.16,0:36:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It should be something...\Nsomething much more extravagant!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.67,0:37:01.17,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,1800)}"Chawanmushi"{Putting in a note to say, this was Mr. Akatsuka's favorite food, it comes up a lot in his work, sometimes as it's own character.}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.28,0:37:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.53,0:37:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That plot twist at the end was so sudden!{That sudden plot twist at the end was so typical!} \NRight, Mr. Akatsuka? {yume's: final twist was outright savage}{Y: 痛烈 as in "intense", not "criticism-worthy". Stale/cliche would be expressed differently. Rewording for a more ambiguous take}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.65,0:37:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You watched it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.34,0:37:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ishimori invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.47,0:37:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Twists are fine and all, but the\Npunchlines to the gags could've been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.55,0:37:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.12,0:37:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gathered to talk about new manga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.83,0:38:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better to research\Nmanga instead of discussing movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.78,0:38:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe movies make \Nimportant research material, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.34,0:38:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't become a proper mangaka\Nif you limit yourself to reading manga alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.68,0:38:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you can't stomach movies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.34,0:38:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I like them. \NBut we'd benefit more from studying drawing! {デッサン}{something more fundamental, like ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.06,0:38:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. \NWe can continue this discussion over dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.91,0:38:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.35,0:38:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka, do you have any money\Nfor food? I've spent mine on movie tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.16,0:38:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you know the answer already.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.89,0:38:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.16,0:38:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent mine on books.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.83,0:38:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.79,0:38:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.75,0:38:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you spent all of your\Nfood money on movies and books?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.51,0:38:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to spend money more consciously!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.15,0:38:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. I'll treat you to dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.87,0:38:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate it, Mr. Tera.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.64,0:38:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thanks.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.84,0:38:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These guys are so intense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.27,0:38:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While I have a home in Tokyo,\Nthey've got no backup options.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.59,0:39:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, they readily spend\Ntheir food money on books and movies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.54,0:39:01.23,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}"Now showing: Swan Lake" {no idea what this is referencing, there's one swan-lake-themed episode of cyborg 009, but it clearly wasn't shown in cinema; probably just an hommage to ishinomori's fondness for swan lake}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.23,0:39:04.38,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Coming next week"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.23,0:39:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems as if they're fooling around, but really,\Nthey're just spending their savings on study materials.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.47,0:39:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta hurry... Gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.44,0:39:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.94,0:39:27.75,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, a national weather forecast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.75,0:39:36.08,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{TLC, some bits are muffled as hell. Translating liberally. "kon'ya wa --teki ni atsui kumo ga -- tame, are sou de, kore sou de, ichiji wa ooame ni naru deshou"; is alright}Tonight, a warm front will roll in, bringing cloudy weather.\NIn areas here and there, prolonged rain is likely at around one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.08,0:39:39.48,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"tokoro ni yotte wa ooyuki ni naru kamoshire to baai ni wa, -- narubeku joubu na ama-- wo youi shita hou ga yoi to, kokoro no oyabun mo itteorimasu"}In some places, it may change into a snowfall.{\i0}{also see https://www.koredeiinoda.net/manga/s_kokoronobosu.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.48,0:39:46.62,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"tokoro ni yotte wa ooyuki ni naru kamoshire to baai ni wa, -- kata wa narubeku joubu na ama-- wo youi shita hou ga yoi to, kokoro no oyabun mo itteorimasu"}As such, Boss Kokoro recommends\Nyou to prepare the appropriate rain gear.{\i0}{雨具}{also see https://www.koredeiinoda.net/manga/s_kokoronobosu.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.62,0:39:50.73,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"kore de denki yohou owatta, --"}This wraps up the weather forecast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.01,0:39:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.00,0:39:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you bought a TV, Mr. Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.00,0:39:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I urgently need you to draw 16 pages...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.86,0:39:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a commission for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.70,0:39:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.30,0:39:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta hurry up, or else I won't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.00,0:39:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! What about Mr. Ishimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.22,0:40:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.62,0:40:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlocked? How careless of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.81,0:40:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Did you want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.42,0:40:23.12,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Standalone TV set"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.70,0:40:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He bought a TV, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.42,0:40:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tera! Mr. Ishimori bought a huge one!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.94,0:40:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A big TV is so much more impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.24,0:40:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was cheaper than I expected.\NSo, when's the deadline?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.84,0:40:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.26,0:40:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take your sweet time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.51,0:40:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten quiet all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.55,0:40:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can finally watch TV in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.96,0:41:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the violin from this speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.90,0:41:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This stereo player is a great\N achievement of our civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.05,0:41:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.42,0:41:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While I don't have a player, I get to work while listening\Nto famous classical and jazz tunes. This is what I call luxury.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.57,0:41:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm not done reading this one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.00,0:41:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Sci-fi is so great, I must say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.67,0:42:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe stretches on endlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.65,0:42:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I prefer him masked.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.24,0:42:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do \Nabout their faces, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.06,0:42:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Try sketching them in various poses first.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.81,0:42:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to flesh out\Nthe supporting roles as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.12,0:42:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.44,0:42:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This story might've been short, but I enjoyed it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.48,0:42:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The children who read manga are no different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.74,0:42:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to draw manga that makes people laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.45,0:42:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, time to put up a curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.13,0:43:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Do you realize how late it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.83,0:43:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good heavens...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.69,0:43:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They've fallen asleep at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.61,0:43:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So they've been sneakily wasting electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.18,0:43:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine servings of ramen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.97,0:43:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.15,0:43:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine servings of ramen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.51,0:44:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving of ramen for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.86,0:44:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TLC, too muffled.; no idea either}Aye! Ten servings, coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.08,0:44:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't waste any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.00,0:44:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And done!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.96,0:44:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.05,0:44:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, time to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.36,0:44:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.31,0:44:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A popular one. Something that sells well.\NThat's one depressive outlook on the world of manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.39,0:44:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider the readers' impressions instead,\Nand how you can express yourself through manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.38,0:44:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you should focus on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.98,0:44:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.58,0:45:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.33,0:45:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to take a fresh start\Nand write a manga centered on comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.64,0:45:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.05,0:45:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.76,0:45:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.87,0:45:16.21,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Akakka-kun"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.82,0:45:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just say it's mediocre.{Well, let's just say it's too immature.}{生煮え}{Y: "immature" applies to people / attitudes, while "mediocre"/"not fleshed out" applies to things. Here, the manga is bland.}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.75,0:45:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and draw the\Nnew manga we already agreed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.47,0:45:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.51,0:45:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, Mr. Akatsuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.25,0:45:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna see a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.03,0:45:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadlines are nearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.95,0:45:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.37,0:45:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.30,0:45:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ishimori has it great.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.21,0:45:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Adventures and experiments...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.36,0:46:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I nearly forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.59,0:46:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.58,0:46:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your share for helping\Nwith my manga the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.88,0:46:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.57,0:46:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I simply\Nbecome Mr. Ishimori's assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.58,0:46:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the shoujo manga you've lent me...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.29,0:46:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.01,0:46:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.67,0:46:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being praised feels nice,\Nbut that isn't the type of manga I want to draw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.44,0:46:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The water's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.13,0:46:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.53,0:46:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.42,0:46:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up so early... Another all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.41,0:46:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.03,0:46:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. My sister's coming to visit.\NI'm off to Ueno to pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.96,0:46:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.77,0:47:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.15,0:47:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.27,0:47:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a stunning beauty in the kitchen just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.88,0:47:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you call a jewel in a dunghill.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.75,0:47:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pretty girl in our humble dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.23,0:47:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.82,0:47:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.74,0:47:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my sister, Yoshie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.26,0:47:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching over my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.93,0:47:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! So it's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.22,0:47:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.43,0:48:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.96,0:48:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! S-So this is y-your sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.81,0:48:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be this shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.69,0:48:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.94,0:48:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is she...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.25,0:48:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.62,0:48:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have enough soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.32,0:48:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need a pot, here's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.99,0:48:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also use our bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.16,0:48:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I could light a fire for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.19,0:48:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your hands off my sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.63,0:48:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.71,0:48:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done with your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.20,0:48:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.42,0:49:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be having a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.39,0:49:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.95,0:49:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.47,0:49:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I can hold a job like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.56,0:49:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've lost all desire to draw manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.09,0:49:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here, Mr. Tera?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.12,0:49:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.93,0:50:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect time to call it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.90,0:50:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still young enough\Nto reconsider my perspectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.93,0:50:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.24,0:50:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.81,0:50:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the manga you've just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.38,0:50:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.19,0:50:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't continue, no matter how hard I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.44,0:50:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd separate this manuscript into five different manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.13,0:50:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins as shoujo, then branches\Ninto sports, comedy, and even action.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.04,0:50:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it overloaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.19,0:50:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You jump from one topic to the next, \Nwhich is why overall consistency suffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.34,0:50:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it—that's how I feel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.11,0:50:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I start to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.70,0:50:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.32,0:50:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can focus on\Neach of these topics separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.89,0:50:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you come to live with us\N in order to become a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.52,0:50:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep trying until your dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.02,0:50:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.76,0:50:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, Akatsuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.85,0:51:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're short on money, right? \NYou can use this for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.81,0:51:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the loan, Mr. Tera.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.19,0:51:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This can last me for a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.58,0:51:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be serious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.88,0:51:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tera...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.74,0:51:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tera, I'll become a\Nproper mangaka against all odds!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.82,0:51:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka, you're looking at it the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.27,0:51:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.75,0:52:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.96,0:52:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are the most\Nknowledgeable about shoujo manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.71,0:52:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.55,0:52:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.14,0:52:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.57,0:52:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.39,0:52:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.02,0:52:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look no further.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.85,0:52:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.86,0:52:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Sonoyama. \NHe writes absurdist manga.{https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%92%E5%B1%B1%E4%BF%8A%E4%BA%8C, also see ナンセンス漫画}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.05,0:52:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.96,0:52:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are many different people\Ninvested in the world of manga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.73,0:52:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And they kept gathering in\Nthis dorm, as if drawn by a magnet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.76,0:53:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The seeds sown by Osamu Tezuka\Nare steadily sprouting one by one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.41,0:53:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{一種の創刊, liberal}That's how it all started.{\i0}{alt. "That's what gave a boost to the manga industry."}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.48,0:53:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.21,0:53:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They're obsessed with\Ncomics day in and day out!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.77,0:53:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What of Japanese literature?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.75,0:53:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop grumbling already.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.06,0:53:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TLC, muffled. "-- wa mishite miru to kekko omoshiroi yo". From context:}If you give it a chance, \Nit's a fun read in its own right. {no idea either, but I sense it's related to hiroii = "broadminded"}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.64,0:53:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your standards have plummeted, too!{lib}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.62,0:53:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.15,0:53:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.72,0:53:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.20,0:54:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though people may cross paths,\Ninevitably there comes the time to say goodbye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.65,0:54:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ishimori's frail older sister\Npassed away at the tender age of 24.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.55,0:54:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A separation so untimely and unbelievable,\Nhe felt like the pain would never end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.71,0:58:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a naturalistic tale \Ntold solely through imagery.{with no speech}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.65,0:58:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to name it Fantasy World.{One of my all-time faves btw. Go read it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.76,0:58:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.86,0:58:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a bit too radical?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.41,0:58:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's great. I like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.67,0:58:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The panel layout is so inventive!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.40,0:58:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And your sister came out so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.07,0:58:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the embodiment of the "adventures\Nand experiments" you're always talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.67,0:58:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ishimori's style is something else, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.10,0:59:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best, too. Can't let him outdo us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.84,0:59:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka...\NAre you working on something fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.56,0:59:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've noted down heaps of ideas.\NI'll expand on them whenever an opportunity arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.52,0:59:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.81,0:59:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.87,0:59:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.76,0:59:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.44,0:59:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My deadline is still a ways off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.50,0:59:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm in a tight spot myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.50,0:59:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hole in the next issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.77,0:59:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.36,1:00:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The planned eight-page gag \Nmanga oneshot fell through...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.78,1:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if anyone could pull an \Nall-nighter and write a replacement...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.36,1:00:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tall order, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.92,1:00:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know the perfect author for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.96,1:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Of course you don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.60,1:00:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You know one?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.74,1:00:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask Mr. Akatsuka to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.09,1:00:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who, me?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.66,1:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His comedic timing is second to none. Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.90,1:00:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, second to none.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.43,1:00:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. Please do your best.\NI'll come to pick it up tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.81,1:00:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.35,1:00:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have it done by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.73,1:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.24,1:00:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.39,1:00:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will he manage to\Ndeliver on his promise, though?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.47,1:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.87,1:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I've got to trust him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.38,1:01:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do I do now, Mr. Ishimori?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.75,1:01:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it turns out to be unfunny?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.74,1:01:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just write a fun one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.23,1:01:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have lots of ideas\Nand characters noted down, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.65,1:01:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.00,1:01:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that. It's too early to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.84,1:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. {"machigai ka", liberal}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.87,1:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.95,1:01:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! Let's go with this!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.10,1:01:40.11,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Terada"
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.79,1:01:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tera, I'll go all out.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.89,1:01:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first ever commission\Nfor the kind of manga I want to write!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.17,1:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hold back, mark my words!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.90,1:01:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Ishimori,\Nwould you listen to my ideas?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.93,1:01:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.83,1:01:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make the protagonist a real brat!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.51,1:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, such-and-such, this and that!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.45,1:02:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What about {\i1}this{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}way? It'd be even more fun!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.66,1:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! It's settled then.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.12,1:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I name it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.94,1:02:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The protagonist is bratty, so...\NHow does Nama-chan sound?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.91,1:02:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.45,1:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you wrap it up overnight?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.09,1:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet! I'll begin right away!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.52,1:02:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This gag is growing stale.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.11,1:02:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.09,1:02:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here goes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.50,1:02:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And done.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.47,1:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is this actually fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.55,1:03:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding my own manga\Nfunny isn't a good metric.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.85,1:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.55,1:03:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done already?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.24,1:03:11.78,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"I Am Nama-chan"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.64,1:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.33,1:03:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show it to\NMr. Fujimoto and Mr. Abiko next!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.96,1:03:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a laugh riot!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.81,1:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, these gags are on a whole other level.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.69,1:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,F-For real? Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.86,1:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my friends may be\Nsimply trying to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.59,1:04:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way too early to relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.54,1:04:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.45,1:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka, you've struck gold at long last!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.32,1:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seems like they're honestly praising me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.68,1:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So... do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.18,1:04:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the manuscript as is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.62,1:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.80,1:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.00,1:05:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't like it all that much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.20,1:05:56.91,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Good fortune comes to those who smile"
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.91,1:06:03.91,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Post"
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.49,1:06:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time went by. The magazine with Mr. Akatsuka's\Npainstakingly-created gag manga was published.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.63,1:06:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akatsuka, your magazine has come!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.45,1:06:09.96,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"Manga King"
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.47,1:06:20.01,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,"New manga series"\N"Nama-chan"
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.01,1:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it just a oneshot? \NThey've decided to serialize it?!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.71,1:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.81,1:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Akatsuka. It's been picked\Nfor serialization right away. That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.94,1:06:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to you, Mr. Tera.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.68,1:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had given up on manga that day...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.21,1:06:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This only proves how talented you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.89,1:06:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's one groundbreaking kind of a talent!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.35,1:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My own manga might be\Ngetting dated in comparison to yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.89,1:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Mr. Tera.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.73,1:06:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up just yet, Akatsuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.31,1:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep drawing manga according to my own values.\NAnd you should follow your personal way of gags.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.25,1:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.56,1:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.75,1:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and effort will definitely pave a way!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.71,1:07:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been able to come\Nthis far thanks to everyone's support.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.87,1:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's more, living in\NTokiwa-sou helped me follow my dreams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.99,1:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should extend my\Nthanks to the dormitory itself, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.52,1:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.27,1:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.83,1:07:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.48,1:07:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.10,1:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.61,1:07:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aku- This is Hatabou's catchphrase! "Hatabou dajo!" The official subs for osokun just TL it as "I'm Hatabou" so that's what it is, but it's of note he's supposed to sound kinda childish/juvenile in that phrasing}I'm Hatabou!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.15,1:08:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheeh!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.09,1:08:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Same as Kokoro Boss' first appearance}Pokkun! Pokkun! Pokkun!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.57,1:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hatabou!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.45,1:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!{"zamasu"}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.34,1:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aku - "BAKA na no da"}You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.53,1:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{おでかけですか、レレレのレー}Are you going out? Rerere-no-re!{see https://www.koredeiinoda.net/manga/s_rererenoojisan.html}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.05,1:08:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Accelerate!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.26,1:08:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.09,1:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.31,1:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.19,1:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold up! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.48,1:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.34,1:09:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These dreams are far from over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.12,1:09:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They offer infinite possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.49,1:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, life in Tokiwa-sou went on,\Nwith youthful dreams crowding the windowsills.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.08,1:09:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what the early 1960s were like.{mid 30th of Showa, as in mid 1955-1965}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.25,1:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, Tokiwa-sou fulfilled\Nits purpose as the bastion of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.64,1:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, it's quietly fading away.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.31,1:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The monument to the mangakas'\Nyouth is vanishing before our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.24,1:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still, are their dreams truly over?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.99,1:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About now, a new generation of authors follows\Nin their footsteps, carrying new dreams in tow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.14,1:10:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dreams never truly end.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.34,1:11:00.65,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,My friend, my good old friend
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.65,1:11:08.91,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,Back then, we lived in this dormitory
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.91,1:11:17.37,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,{mou sugu kiete, nakunarisou da}It's about to disappear once and for all
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.37,1:11:25.50,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,But our memories will never fade
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.52,1:12:00.99,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,Next time we meet, why don't we go on a trip \Nsomewhere far away, just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.99,1:12:17.91,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,Even my wife doesn't mind me leaving\Nher alone if she knows I'm meeting with you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.11,1:12:26.39,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,My friend, my good old friend
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.39,1:12:30.53,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,I am fine
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.53,1:12:34.17,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,I am doing just fine
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.83,1:12:43.44,Singing - top,,0,0,0,,My friend, my good old friend
